com.orsoncharts.data

Interface PieDataset3D

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Dataset3D, KeyedValues<java.lang.Number>, Values<java.lang.Number>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StandardPieDataset3D

    public interface PieDataset3D
extends KeyedValues<java.lang.Number>, Dataset3D
    The interface through which the PiePlot3D class obtains data for pie charts. The interface defines methods for reading data only, not for updating the data (however, classes that implement the interface will typically provide their own methods for updating the dataset).

    • Method Summary

      • Methods inherited from interface com.orsoncharts.data.KeyedValues

        getIndex, getKey, getKeys, getValue

      • Methods inherited from interface com.orsoncharts.data.Values

        getDoubleValue, getItemCount, getValue

      • Methods inherited from interface com.orsoncharts.data.Dataset3D

        addChangeListener, hasListener, removeChangeListener
